attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: A developer’s dream on South Boston’s East Side—act fast. This rare package includes 611 East 7th Street, a two-family, and next door 607 MLS#, offering 3,474+ sq ft of prime land with off-street parking and 5 deeded parking spaces in one of the city’s hottest markets. Ideal for a luxury condo conversion, upscale rentals, or a signature single-family, this combined offering delivers the size, location, and demand every developer seeks. Steps to beaches, the renovated Curley Community Center, acclaimed dining, and nightlife, with quick access to Route 90, I-93, Downtown Boston, and just 15 minutes to Logan Airport or the Seaport. South Boston’s market is hitting record prices, seize this high-demand opportunity. Seller prefers to convey both properties together. Buyers to perform all due diligence.
